Line.text: Mmh... I need to slide something in here to open the door.
Do I have something like that yet?
It's locked... How can I open it?
Hey, take a look at the right. Do we need to slide something in there?
Yes I got it!
Now we can get out!
Thanks for playing the demo!
See you later! Cheers!
Mmh... What is this?
This looks like some kind of claw...?
Hey... There's a key here! We can use this to escape!
Wonderful, go get it!
Okay... This fire is fake right? Let me reach for it...
AAHUAHUAUAUAGHGH THAT'S HOT.
You idiot! Why didn't you notice the warmth earlier?!
Owh... Well... Let's find another way to grab this.
With this trash picker I can probably reach it...!
I got it.
Woah! Good job!
Thank you-- Owwha It's still hot!
It won't budge. I will need a key to open this.
This key should do it!
... Yes!
What is this triangular shape doing here?
Oh. It might be a shape for the puzzle.
What kind of oddity is this?
Mmhh... It looks like someone cracked open another's skull and their brains are spatting out.
I think I will never ask you again.
But hey, we have to investigate everything. Maybe there's like a hidden locker behind this painting or something.
Well... I doubt that but let me take the painting anyway...
A display showing 4 icons...
I did it.
Good job.
Ohh? I think this appeared when I finished the puzzle.
Grab it!
Hey, isn't that a red shape I need for the other puzzle?
Yes I got it!
... I think it fell on the floor.
This shape fell out of the puzzle.
picking it up...
Oh this looks like a shape puzzle I used to play this as a kid.
Wow, you had such an interesting life.
Wait... How did you... Our memories were wiped.
Wh- You're right... How did I.. Oh god I don't know.
That's really suspicious... But for some reason I don't feel like you're lying... I think I've seen this puzzle before too.
Of course I'm not lying! Anyhow... We can't do this puzzle right now... Look, the shapes are missing.
Yeah... you're right... Maybe they're lying somewhere around here?
Alright, We got all the pieces now
Hurry up and put them in then!
Yeah yeah...
This goes here... That goes there...
Last one there and.......
All done!
Oh... Something fell out of the puzzle.
Another key....?
Let's see what we can open with the key.
It won't budge. The right key would open it.
I think we've investigated everything except beyond this door.
Well, hurry up and open it! I want to see what's inside!
Okay! It should be open now.
A keycard!
Hey... I don't feel alright in this room...
It's like a studio... It looks like staff sat here to monitor us.
Oh my god...
What the fuck is this facility?!
Egh, let's get out with this keycard. We might even be able to each other areas in the lobby.
Right. Let's go.
Mhh...
This door won't budge.
Don't waste your time with me! Hurry up so we can get out of here!
Ni Hao! Watashi Wa Robotto-San-Kun
